item.title: CVE-2023-36926|2023-08-08T00:38:12.784Z -- sap_se -- sap%20host%20agent
item.description: Due to missing authentication check in SAP Host Agent - version 7.22, an unauthenticated attacker can set an undocumented parameter to a particular compatibility value and in turn call read functions. This allows the attacker to gather some non-sensitive information about the server.Â There is no impact on integrity or availability.
